<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 08:11:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>新喀里多尼亚在投票改革骚乱中召集更多警察</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/new-caledonia-calls-in-more-police-amid-riots-over-voting-reform/articleshow/110110032.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110110032.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;新喀里多尼亚因投票制度的改变而面临暴力抗议，导致机场关闭和宵禁。高级专员报告了警察受伤和财产损失的情况。马克龙旨在增强法国影响力，议员们正在讨论修正案。法国政府一直在就亏损的新喀里多尼亚镍行业的救助计划进行谈判，其中包括承诺向欧洲电池供应链供应，但由于当前的政治紧张局势，谈判陷入僵局。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 07:50:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/new-caledonia-calls-in-more-police-amid-riots-over-voting-reform/articleshow/110110032.cms</guid></item><item><title>封锁西雅图-塔科马机场附近道路的亲巴勒斯坦示威者不认罪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/pro-palestinian-demonstrators-who-blocked-road-near-sea-tac-airport-plead-not-guilty/articleshow/110109556.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110109556.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;西塔科机场的 37 名亲巴勒斯坦抗议者对轻罪指控表示无罪。他们呼吁以色列-哈马斯战争立即停火，轻罪可判处最高 90 天的监禁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 07:35:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/pro-palestinian-demonstrators-who-blocked-road-near-sea-tac-airport-plead-not-guilty/articleshow/110109556.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴控克什米尔安全部队发射催泪瓦斯，造成 3 人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/3-killed-in-firing-and-teargas-shelling-by-security-forces-in-pakistan-occupied-kashmir/articleshow/110109246.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110109246.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;总理批准 230 亿卢比的补贴，穆扎法拉巴德冲突造成 3 人死亡。由 JAAC 领导的针对电费和小麦补贴的抗议活动。扎尔达里敦促在暴力冲突和僵局中通过对话和平解决问题。周六，这个有争议的地区还发生了警察和维权活动人士之间的冲突，导致至少一名警察死亡，100 多人受伤，其中大部分是警察。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 07:28:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/3-killed-in-firing-and-teargas-shelling-by-security-forces-in-pakistan-occupied-kashmir/articleshow/110109246.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人纪念被剥夺土地76周年，加沙可能会发生更大的灾难</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinians-mark-76-years-of-dispossession-as-a-potentially-even-larger-catastrophe-unfolds-in-gaza/articleshow/110108525.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110108525.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴勒斯坦人在加沙危机中纪念大灾难，强调 1948 年阿以战争引发的持续斗争。以色列拒绝巴勒斯坦人返回家园的权利加剧了这场冲突，导致了严重的难民危机和加沙的毁灭性后果。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 07:12:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinians-mark-76-years-of-dispossession-as-a-potentially-even-larger-catastrophe-unfolds-in-gaza/articleshow/110108525.cms</guid></item><item><title>南太平洋法国岛屿领土发生骚乱后，新喀里多尼亚实施宵禁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/curfew-is-imposed-in-new-caledonia-after-unrest-wracks-french-island-territory-in-south-pacific/articleshow/110108527.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110108527.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;为了应对暴力骚乱，新喀里多尼亚在努美阿实施宵禁，安全部队受伤。反对投票改革的抗议引发了骚乱，造成破坏和逮捕。高级专员的声明称，没有发生严重平民伤亡的报道。高级专员表示，从当地时间周二晚上 6 点开始，努美阿的宵禁将持续至少 12 小时，如有必要，可能会延长。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 07:12:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/curfew-is-imposed-in-new-caledonia-after-unrest-wracks-french-island-territory-in-south-pacific/articleshow/110108527.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度尼西亚洪水死亡人数上升至50人，27人失踪：灾害机构</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indonesia-flood-death-toll-rises-to-50-with-27-missing-disaster-agency/articleshow/110099405.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110099405.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;印度尼西亚雅加达山洪暴发和寒冷熔岩流造成的死亡人数已达 50 人，仍有 27 人失踪。这场由印度尼西亚西部火山引发的灾难还造成 37 人受伤，3,396 人被疏散。大雨导致苏门答腊岛两个地区发生洪水，带来了马拉皮山的火山灰和岩石。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 02:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indonesia-flood-death-toll-rises-to-50-with-27-missing-disaster-agency/articleshow/110099405.cms</guid></item><item><title>沃尔玛将解雇数百名员工并重新安置其他员工：报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/walmart-to-lay-off-hundreds-of-corporate-staff-and-relocate-others-reports/articleshow/110106612.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110106612.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据称，美国跨国零售公司沃尔玛将削减数百个公司职位，并敦促许多远程员工搬到办公地点。据《华尔街日报》周一报道，这家零售巨头还要求其较小办公室的员工搬迁到其他中心枢纽。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 06:29:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/walmart-to-lay-off-hundreds-of-corporate-staff-and-relocate-others-reports/articleshow/110106612.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国公民因使用淫秽语言在俄罗斯被拘留：消息来源</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/us-citizen-detained-in-russia-for-using-obscene-language-sources/articleshow/110105206.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110105206.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;安杰洛·约瑟夫·塔拉里科四世 (Angelo Joseph Talarico the Fourth) 是一名美国公民，因在警方搜查期间使用猥亵语言而因轻微流氓行为而在莫斯科被拘留。尽管他否认宣誓，但他还是被判有罪，并失去了拘留上诉。美国警告其公民不要前往俄罗斯，并给出了一系列理由，包括“俄罗斯政府安全官员可能会骚扰和单独拘留美国公民”以及该法律的任意执行。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 05:46:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/us-citizen-detained-in-russia-for-using-obscene-language-sources/articleshow/110105206.cms</guid></item><item><title>新喀里多尼亚骚乱中向安全部队“开枪”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/shots-fired-at-security-forces-in-new-caledonia-riots/articleshow/110104585.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110104585.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;新喀里多尼亚的骚乱导致向宪兵开枪、纵火袭击、抢劫以及与警察的冲突。反对投票改革的抗议引发了宵禁。 1998 年协议的选民名单问题引发了骚乱和逮捕。据当局称，共有 36 人被捕，30 名警察受伤。新喀里多尼亚政府在昨晚的骚乱后呼吁“理性和冷静”，并呼吁“所有喀里多尼亚人表现出责任感”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 05:23:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/shots-fired-at-security-forces-in-new-caledonia-riots/articleshow/110104585.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦：所有国有企业将进行私有化</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-all-state-owned-enterprises-to-undergo-privatisation/articleshow/110103778.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110103778.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 05:15:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-all-state-owned-enterprises-to-undergo-privatisation/articleshow/110103778.cms</guid></item><item><title>迈克尔·科恩将面临特朗普律师的严酷盘问</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/michael-cohen-to-face-bruising-cross-examination-by-trumps-lawyers/articleshow/110103332.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110103332.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;科恩的审判证词揭露了特朗普在 2016 年竞选期间参与了一项封口费计划，以压制破坏性的报道，这可能会增加特朗普的法律风险。此案的展开伴随着对科恩的可信度以及特朗普与付款的直接联系的严格审查。科恩是迄今为止检方最重要的证人。 “我们需要阻止这件事传出去，”科恩援引特朗普的话说，他指的是色情演员斯托米·丹尼尔斯(Stormy Daniels)十年前与特朗普发生性接触的经历。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 04:45:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/michael-cohen-to-face-bruising-cross-examination-by-trumps-lawyers/articleshow/110103332.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国登山者在尼泊尔马卡鲁山身亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/french-climber-dies-on-nepals-mt-makalu/articleshow/110103353.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110103353.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;探险组织者周二表示，一名法国登山者在世界第五高峰马卡鲁峰死亡，这是今年春季登山季节的第二起死亡事件，而且两起死亡事件都发生在同一座山上。数百名登山者涌向这个喜马拉雅山国家，世界上 14 座最高峰中的 8 座都位于这个国家，在春季登山季节，气温温暖，风通常很平静。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 04:46:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/french-climber-dies-on-nepals-mt-makalu/articleshow/110103353.cms</guid></item><item><title>州长称乌克兰袭击俄罗斯别尔哥罗德房屋受损</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/houses-damaged-in-ukraine-attack-on-russias-belgorod-governor-says/articleshow/110101680.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110101680.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰对别尔哥罗德的空袭造成人员伤亡和财产损失。州长报告一名人员伤亡。导弹碎片造成人员伤亡。基辅在持续的战争中瞄准了俄罗斯的基础设施。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 03:43:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/houses-damaged-in-ukraine-attack-on-russias-belgorod-governor-says/articleshow/110101680.cms</guid></item><item><title>调查发现，欧盟 LGBTIQ 群体面临的歧视较少，但暴力却较多</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/lgbtiq-people-in-eu-face-less-discrimination-more-violence-survey-finds/articleshow/110102588.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110102588.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;欧盟调查显示，欧洲针对 LGBTIQ 人群的歧视有所减少，但暴力行为却有所增加。尽管取得了进展，但欺凌和骚扰等挑战仍然存在，这凸显出需要一个更安全的环境来公开识别该地区的个人身份。大约 36% 的欧盟受访者表示，在最新调查的前一年，他们至少在生活的一个领域感到受到歧视，因为他们是 LGBTIQ，这一比例低于上一次调查的 42%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 04:18:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/lgbtiq-people-in-eu-face-less-discrimination-more-violence-survey-finds/articleshow/110102588.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦总理谢赫巴兹批准向巴控克朗提供 8260 万美元用于平息骚乱</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-clears-cash-to-calm-pok/articleshow/110093460.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110093460.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦总理谢巴兹·谢里夫批准向巴控克什米尔 (PoK) 拨款约 8,260 万美元，以解决因提高电价、面粉价格和税收而引发的暴力抗议活动。抗议活动导致一名警察死亡，另有 90 人受伤。这场骚乱给在该地区驻有大量人员的巴基斯坦军队带来了挑战。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 18:18:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-clears-cash-to-calm-pok/articleshow/110093460.cms</guid></item><item><title>“未经授权的人”在俄罗斯伏尔加格勒附近使货运列车脱轨</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/unauthorised-persons-derail-freight-train-near-russias-volgograd-agencies/articleshow/110101964.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110101964.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯新闻机构周二称，货运列车车厢在俄罗斯伏尔加格勒地区脱轨，“未经授权的人员”被指控造成了这起事件。据塔斯社报道，“由于未经授权人员的干预，伏尔加格勒地区科特卢班车站发生货运列车车厢脱轨事件。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 03:54:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/unauthorised-persons-derail-freight-train-near-russias-volgograd-agencies/articleshow/110101964.cms</guid></item><item><title>布林肯对乌克兰进行暗访，以表明美国在俄罗斯袭击加剧之际对基辅的支持</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/blinken-makes-unannounced-visit-to-ukraine-to-show-us-support-for-kyiv-as-russian-attacks-intensify/articleshow/110100198.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110100198.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周二出人意料地访问基辅，重申美国对乌克兰应对俄罗斯加剧攻击的支持。在他此行之前，国会最近批准了期待已久的对外援助计划。批准的对乌克兰的600亿美元援助计划将主要集中于补充耗尽的火炮和防空系统。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 02:52:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/blinken-makes-unannounced-visit-to-ukraine-to-show-us-support-for-kyiv-as-russian-attacks-intensify/articleshow/110100198.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登签署禁止进口俄罗斯核反应堆燃料的法律</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-signs-into-law-ban-on-russian-nuclear-reactor-fuel-imports/articleshow/110101195.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110101195.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 03:25:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-signs-into-law-ban-on-russian-nuclear-reactor-fuel-imports/articleshow/110101195.cms</guid></item><item><title>封口费审判：迈克尔·科恩针对特朗普的谴责性证词</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hush-money-trial-michael-cohens-damning-testimony-against-trump/articleshow/110099765.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110099765.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普的前掮客迈克尔·科恩周一告诉陪审员，这位共和党总统候选人亲自批准了一笔封口费，以埋葬一名色情明星的性遭遇故事，以免破坏他2016年的竞选活动。科恩说，特朗普告诉他“就这么做吧” ，指示他找出向成人电影女演员斯托米·丹尼尔斯支付 13 万美元的最佳方式，以使其对 2006 年所谓的私通保持沉默，但他否认了这一点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 02:27:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hush-money-trial-michael-cohens-damning-testimony-against-trump/articleshow/110099765.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国迫使与中国有联系的公司出售美国导弹发射井附近的土地</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-to-force-china-linked-firm-to-sell-land-near-us-missile-silos/articleshow/110098804.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110098804.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 01:13:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-to-force-china-linked-firm-to-sell-land-near-us-missile-silos/articleshow/110098804.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>